PER TROVARE GLI ERRORI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #ERRORE#
PER TROVARE I WARNING, CERCARE LA STRINGA #WARNING#
PER TROVARE I DUPLICATI, CERCARE LA STRINGA #DUPLICATO#
*******************************************************

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_PERIODO CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_NUMERATORE CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   R_SERIE CHAR(2),
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   DATA_INZ DATETIME,
   DATA_FINE DATETIME,
   GEN_AUTOM_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   RIEL_GIA_ARCHIV CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   TIPO_ELABORAZ CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   TIPO_DIAGNOSTICA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_PERIODO CHAR(6) NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_NUMERATORE CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   R_SERIE CHAR(2),
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   DATA_INZ DATETIME,
   DATA_FINE DATETIME,
   GEN_AUTOM_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   RIEL_GIA_ARCHIV CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   TIPO_ELABORAZ CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   TIPO_DIAGNOSTICA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CHIAVE_PRIM ON THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_STORICO ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID_AZIENDA, ID_STORICO)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.SOSTITUTIVA_STOR TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THIP.SOST_RES
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_RIGA INTEGER NOT NULL,
   BATCH_JOB_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ID_ANNO_DOC CHAR(6),
   ID_NUMERO_DOC CHAR(10),
   STATO_STP_DOC CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   STATO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'A',
   R_DOC_DGT BIGINT,
   R_VER_DGT SMALLINT,
   STATO_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(15),
   STATO_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(15),
   STATO_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   ESITO_PRE VARCHAR(500),
   AZIONE_POSSIBILE CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   AZIONE_ESEGUITA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ESITO_POST VARCHAR(500),
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)

Tablespace non specificato per la tabella, usato quello di default.
CREATE TABLE THIP.SOST_RES
(
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_STORICO INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ID_RIGA INTEGER NOT NULL,
   BATCH_JOB_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   TIPO_DOCUMENTO CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ID_ANNO_DOC CHAR(6),
   ID_NUMERO_DOC CHAR(10),
   STATO_STP_DOC CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   STATO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'A',
   R_DOC_DGT BIGINT,
   R_VER_DGT SMALLINT,
   STATO_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_MODELLO_RPT CHAR(15),
   STATO_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_DESCR_STP_DGT CHAR(15),
   STATO_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   R_TIPO_DOC_DGT CHAR(10),
   ESITO_PRE VARCHAR(500),
   AZIONE_POSSIBILE CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   AZIONE_ESEGUITA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
   ESITO_POST VARCHAR(500),
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX SOST_RES_PK ON THIP.SOST_RES (ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_STORICO ASC, ID_RIGA ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.SOST_RES ADD PRIMARY KEY  (ID_AZIENDA, ID_STORICO, ID_RIGA)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.SOST_RES TO PUBLIC

DROP VIEW FINANCE.THCAQV2 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THCAQV2 (
    T01CD,
    DIZSTATO,
    DIZUTCRE,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZHHCRE,
    DIZUTAGG,
    DIZDTAGG,
    DIZHHAGG,
    ID_CAU_RIG_DOCACQ,
    TCAQDSNOR,
    TCAQDSRID,
    TCAQDSRIC,
    TCAQDTINI,
    TCAQDTFIN,
    THCAQFLG,
    T12CD,
    T12DSNOR,
    T12DSRID
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.ID_CAU_RIG_DOCACQ,
    T1.TCAQDSNOR,
    T1.TCAQDSRID,
    T1.TCAQDSRIC,
    T1.TCAQDTINI,
    T1.TCAQDTFIN,
    T1.THCAQFLG,
    T1.T12CD,
    T2.T12DSNOR,
    T2.T12DSRID
FROM
      FINANCE.THCAQPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT12PT T2
     ON  T1.T12CD = T2.T12CD

DROP VIEW FINANCE.THRDAV4
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.THRDAV4 AS 
SELECT     
    T1.ID_AZIENDA,
    T1.ID_ANNO_DOC,
    T1.ID_NUMERO_DOC,
    T1.ID_RIGA_DOC,
    T1.ID_DET_RIGA_DOC,
    T1.STATO_AVANZAMENTO,
    COALESCE(T1.R_ARTICOLO, ' ') AS R_ARTICOLO,
    COALESCE(T1.VLR_IMPOSTA, 0) AS VLR_IMPOSTA,
    COALESCE(T1.R_ASSOG_IVA, ' ') AS R_ASSOG_IVA,
    COALESCE(T1.DATA_CONSEG_RCS, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_CONSEG_RCS,
    COALESCE(T1.DATA_CONSEG_CFM, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_CONSEG_CFM,
    COALESCE(T1.VALORE_RIGA, 0) AS VALORE_RIGA,
    COALESCE(T1.R_MAGAZZINO, ' ') AS R_MAGAZZINO,
    T1.NO_FATTURA,
    T1.TIPO_RIGA, 
    T1.COL_CONTABILITA, 
    COALESCE(T1.DATA_BOLLA, CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) AS DATA_BOLLA, 
    T1.STATO, 
    COALESCE(T1.R_CAU_RIG_DOCACQ, ' ') AS R_CAU_RIG_DOCACQ 
FROM THIP.DOC_ACQ_RIG T1

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.THRDAV4 TO PUBLIC

    BC1RISBI,
    BC1RICOL,
    BC2RICOL,
    BC3RICOL,
    BC4RICOL,
    BC5RICOL,
    BCVFLSEG
) AS

SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.SBCCSDBC,
    T1.BC1NATCO,
    T1.BC1SZBIL,
    T1.BC1COLN1,
    T1.BC2COLN2,
    T1.BC3COLN3,
    T1.BC4COLN4,
    T1.BC5COLN5,
    T1.VOCCD,
    T2.DIZSTATO,
    T2.VOCDSNOR,
    T2.VOCNAVOC,
    T2.VOCSECON,
    T2.VOCCLFOV,
    T1.T63COSBC,
    T1.T63FLCFB,
    T3.T63DESNO,
    T3.T63DSRID,
    T1.BCVFSSAV,
    T1.BC1RINAC,
    T1.BC1RISBI,
    T1.BC1RICOL,
    T1.BC2RICOL,
    T1.BC3RICOL,
    T1.BC4RICOL,
    T1.BC5RICOL,
    T1.BCVFLSEG
FROM
      FINANCE.BCBCVPT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT63PT T3
     ON  T1.T01CD = T3.T01CD AND
         T1.T63COSBC = T3.T63COSBC AND
         T1.T63FLCFB = T3.T63FLCFB
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBVOCPT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.VOCCD = T2.VOCCD

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BTSBPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT
(
   DIZSTATO CHAR(1),
   DIZUTCRE CHAR(8),
   DIZDTCRE DATETIME,
   DIZHHCRE DATETIME,
   DIZUTAGG CHAR(8),
   DIZDTAGG DATETIME,
   DIZHHAGG DATETIME,
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   TT01CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   T40CD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   TSBDATA DATETIME NOT NULL,
   TSBSALDO NUMERIC(17,2),
   T29CD CHAR(4)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BTSBPT ADD CONSTRAINT BTSBPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD, TT01CD, T40CD, TSBDATA )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BTSBPT TO PUBLIC
DROP TABLE FINANCE.TYRTBPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.TYRTBPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.

(
   WPRBNLOG NUMERIC(9,0) NOT NULL,
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   T96CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   TT01CD CHAR(8) NOT NULL,
   TT01DSNOR CHAR(35),
   T40CD CHAR(5) NOT NULL,
   T40DSNOR CHAR(35),
   T29CD CHAR(4),
   YRTBSATE NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSTNR NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBNR NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBCA NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBSBEF NUMERIC(17,2),
   YRTBDTSA DATETIME,
   YRTBDELT NUMERIC(17,2)
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.TYRTBPT ADD CONSTRAINT TYRTBPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (WPRBNLOG, T01CD, T96CD, TT01CD, T40CD )

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35658/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BTFINVG 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BTFINVG AS 
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.TT01CD,
    T1.T40CD
FROM FINANCE.BBT40VL T1 
INNER JOIN FINANCE.BTT05PT T2 ON T1.TT05CD = T2.TT05CD
WHERE T2.TT05CALI >= '20'

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/35726/primrose/script/01Viste.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.GWWS1V01 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.GWWS1V01 (
    GWS1NRLG,
    T01CD,
    T96CD,
    T96DSNOR,
    T96DSRID,
    DIZDTCRE,
    DIZFLGPD,
    DIZTIPEL,
    DIZTIPST,
    DIZESBCH,
    GT02CD,
    GT02DSNO,
    GAT0CD,
    GAT0DSNO,
    GT03CD,
    GT03DSNO,
    GAT1CD,
    GAT1DSNO,
    GAT2CD,
    GAT2DSNO,
    GS01CD,
    GWS1OGQ2,
    GWS1OGQ3,
    GWS1OGQ4,
    GWS1OGQ5,
    GC25DSNO,
    GWS1DNQ2,
    GWS1DNQ3,
    GWS1DNQ4,
    GWS1DNQ5,
    GC34CHTO,
    GT01CD,
    GC34CD,
    GC34DSNO,
    GC34DSBR,
    GC36CD,
    GC36DSBR,
    GC36DSNO,
    T97CD,
    REASST01,
    REASST96,
    REASSSTP,
    REASDSTP,
    GFL0CDFL,
    GFL0DSFL
) AS

SELECT
    T1.GWS1NRLG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T2.T96DSNOR,
    T2.T96DSRID,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.GT02CD,
    T1.GT02DSNO,
    T1.GAT0CD,
    T1.GAT0DSNO,
    T1.GT03CD,
    T1.GT03DSNO,
    T1.GAT1CD,
    T1.GAT1DSNO,
    T1.GAT2CD,
    T1.GAT2DSNO,
    T1.GS01CD,
    T1.GWS1OGQ2,
    T1.GWS1OGQ3,
    T1.GWS1OGQ4,
    T1.GWS1OGQ5,
    T1.GC25DSNO,
    T1.GWS1DNQ2,
    T1.GWS1DNQ3,
    T1.GWS1DNQ4,
    T1.GWS1DNQ5,
    T1.GC34CHTO,
    T1.GT01CD,
    T1.GC34CD,
    T3.GC34DSNO,
    T3.GC34DSBR,
    T1.GC36CD,
    T4.GC36DSBR,
    T4.GC36DSNO,
    T1.T97CD,
    T1.REASST01,
    T1.REASST96,
    T1.REASSSTP,
    T5.STPDSNOR,
    T1.GFL0CDFL,
    T6.GFL0DSFL
FROM
      FINANCE.GWWS1PT T1
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GFL0PT T6
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T6.GT01CD AND
         T1.GFL0CDFL = T6.GFL0CDFL
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.SVSTPPT T5
     ON  T1.REASST01 = T5.T01CD AND
         T1.REASST96 = T5.T96CD AND
         T1.REASSSTP = T5.STPCD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GC36PT T4
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T4.GT01CD AND
         T1.GC36CD = T4.GC36CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.GC34PT T3
     ON  T1.GT01CD = T3.GT01CD AND
         T1.GC34CD = T3.GC34CD
         LEFT OUTER JOIN
         FINANCE.BBT96PT T2
     ON  T1.T01CD = T2.T01CD AND
         T1.T96CD = T2.T96CD

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BBANRVG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BBANRVG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BBANRVG AS
	SELECT 
	T1.ANACD,
	T1.ANRCD,
	T1.ANRNOCON,
	T1.ANRFUAZI,
	T1.ANRNOLIB,
	T1.ANRTELEF,
	T1.ANRFAX,
	T1.ANRININT,
	T1.ANICD,
	T1.DIZSTATO,
	T2.R_TITOLO,
	T2.COGNOME,
	T2.NOME,
	T2.NUM_CELLULARE,
	T2.R_MANSIONE,
	T2.UNITA_ORGAN,
	T2.RESPONSABILE,
	T2.ASSISTENTE,
	T2.AZIONE_MKTNG,
	T2.DECISORE,
	T2.R_INDIRIZZO_PSN,
	T2.DATA_NASCITA,
	T2.CONIUGE,
	T2.FIGLI,
	T2.R_UTENTE_CRZ,
	T2.R_UTENTE_AGG,
	T2.TIMESTAMP_CRZ,
	T2.TIMESTAMP_AGG,
	T2.PATENTE_NUM,
	T2.ENTE_RILASCIO,
	T2.DATA_RILASCIO,
	T2.DATA_SCADENZA,
	T2.R_TIPO_PATENTE,
	T2.ID_RUB_SIST_EST
	FROM 
		FINANCE.BBANRPT T1
		LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.RUBRICHE_EXT T2 
		ON T1.ANACD = T2.ID_ANAGRAFICO AND T1.ANRCD  = T2.ID_SEQUENZA_RUB

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BWWBCV3 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BWWBCV3' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BWWBCV3 AS
SELECT
    T1.WBCNRLOG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T96CD,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZFLGPD,
    T1.DIZTIPEL,
    T1.DIZTIPST,
    T1.DIZESBCH,
    T1.WBCFESCV,
    T1.WBCFGMPC,
    T1.WBCFLTEL,
    T1.WBCFSPAT,
    T1.SBCCSDBC,
    T1.T64COPBC,
    T1.WBCFRCS
FROM FINANCE.BWWBCPT T1

DROP VIEW FINANCE.GFL0VG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.GFL0VG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.GFL0VG AS
SELECT
    T1.GT01CD,
    T1.DIZSTATO,
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.GFL0CDFL,
    T1.GFL0DSFL,
    T1.GFL0DSRD,
    T1.GFL0DSRC,
    T1.GFL0AUTM,
    T1.GFL0UTIL
FROM FINANCE.GFL0PT T1
WHERE T1.GFL0AUTM = '1'

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BYYEAVG 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BYYEAVG AS 
SELECT
    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.WEANRLOG,
    T1.DIFANRFD,
    T1.DIFNRPEA,
    T1.DIFDTSTA,
    T1.CCPRASOC,
    T1.CCPRASO2,
    T1.CCPPAIVA,
    T1.CCPPFGIU,
    T1.CCPPFCOG,
    T1.CCPPFNOM,
    T1.CCPPFDTN,
    T1.CCPPFSES,
    T1.CCPPFCOM,
    T1.CCPPFPRN,
    T1.CCPPFNAN,
    T1.CCPDFINF,
    T1.CCPDFCAP,
    T1.CCPDFLOC,
    T1.CCPNAZIO,
    T1.CCPPROVI,
    T1.CCPTELEF,
    T1.CCPNUFAX,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.FORDOGAN,
    T1.ANARASOC,
    T1.ANARASO2,
    T1.ANAPAIVA,
    T1.ANAINDIR,
    T1.ANAINDI2,
    T1.ANACAP,
    T1.ANALOCAL,
    T1.ANAININT,
    T1.ANAFAX,
    T1.ANATELEF,
    T1.T35CD,
    T1.T34CD,
    T1.T79UNAOP,
    T1.T79IMUOP,
    T1.T79OPFAC,
    T1.T79IMOFC,
    T1.T79OPCNP,
    T1.T79DTPIN,
    T1.T79DTPFI,
    T1.YEANRLG1,
    T1.YSEARLG2,
    T1.T33CD,
    T1.YEAT33L2,
    T1.YEAT33CL,
    T1.YEACDFOR,
    T1.DIATPFOR,
    T1.BYYEACFF,
    T1.CCPCOFIS,
    T1.DITIPRSF,
    T1.WEADINTE,
    CHAR(T1.YEAPROIN) AS YEAPROIN,
    T1.YEAPRDOC,
    T1.CCHCFISC,
    T1.CCHCFSSR,
    T1.T97NUTIL,
    T1.CCHCONOM,
    T1.CCHNOME,
    T1.CCHSESSO,
    T1.CCHDTNAS,
    T1.CCHCONAS,
    T1.T76CD,
    T1.CCPININT,
    T1.T79NOTA,
    T1.BYYEAPRR,
    T1.T79ANRFD,
    T1.ANACOFIS,
    T1.ANACOGNO,
    T1.ANANOME,
    T1.ANASESSO,
    T1.DITFIDIC,
    T1.WEADIVAP,
    T1.CCPTGPLI,
    T1.YEAESPOR,
    T1.YEACECEE,
    T1.YEACESMA,
    T1.YEAOPASS,
    T1.YEAOPSTR,
    T1.DITCDFIS,
    T1.DITDTIMP,
    T1.DITFIINT,
    CHAR(T1.ENCPRDIC) AS ENCPRDIC,
    T1.ENCPRDOC,
    T1.BYYEAFCO,
    T1.T79CD,
    T1.EDIPATHP,
    (
	COALESCE((SELECT SUM(A.DICIMUTI) FROM FINANCE.BCEA1PT A WHERE A.T01CD = T1.T01CD AND A.DIFANRFD = T1.DIFANRFD AND A.DIFNRPEA = T1.DIFNRPEA AND A.FORCD = T1.FORCD),0)
    ) AS DICIMUTI,
    T1.DICDTFIN, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (T1.DICDTFIN IS NULL) THEN '1'  
      WHEN (T1.DICDTFIN=CONVERT(DATETIME, '1753-01-01', 120)) THEN '1' 
      ELSE '2'  END
     ) AS YEAICO1 
FROM FINANCE.BYYEAPT T1 

DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCEDIVG 
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCEDIVG' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCEDIVG AS

    T1.DIZUTCRE,
    T1.DIZDTCRE,
    T1.DIZHHCRE,
    T1.DIZUTAGG,
    T1.DIZDTAGG,
    T1.DIZHHAGG,
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.WEANRLOG,
    T1.ENCSTATO,
    T1.T79CD,
    T1.DIFANRFD,
    T1.DIFDTSTA,
    T1.YEACDFOR,
    T1.DIATPFOR,
    T1.DITIPRSF,
    T1.WEADINTE,
    T1.CCHCFISC,
    T1.CCHCFSSR,
    T1.DITFIDIC,
    T1.WEADIVAP,
    T1.CCPTGPLI,
    T1.YEAESPOR,
    T1.YEACECEE,
    T1.YEACESMA,
    T1.YEAOPASS,
    T1.YEAOPSTR,
    T1.DITCDFIS,
    T1.DITDTIMP,
    T1.DITFIINT,
    CHAR(T1.ENCPRDIC) AS ENCPRDIC,
    T1.ENCPRDOC,
    T1.BYYEAFCO,
    T1.EDIPATHP
FROM FINANCE.BCEDIPT T1

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36005/primrose/script/02VisteBG.TDDML.
DROP VIEW FINANCE.BCMOTV11 
CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCMOTV11 AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.T09CD,
    T1.MOVNUREG,
    T1.MOVTCLFO,
    T1.MOVDTDOC,
    T1.MOVNDORI,
    T1.CLICD,
    T1.FORCD,
    T1.T07CD,
    T1.MOVNPIVA
FROM FINANCE.BCMOTPT T1
WHERE
  ( ( T1.MOVTCLFO = '1' ) OR  ( T1.MOVTCLFO = '2' ) )

DROP TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIXPT' di tipo tabella, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT
(
   T01CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   RIEDTCHC DATETIME NOT NULL,
   RIENPCHC NUMERIC(3,0) NOT NULL,
   T06CD CHAR(3) NOT NULL
)  ON 'FINANCE4'
ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCRIXPT ADD CONSTRAINT BCRIXPT_IX PRIMARY KEY (T01CD,RIEDTCHC,RIENPCHC,T06CD )
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCRIXPT TO PUBLIC

#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'FINANCE.BCRIXVA' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


CREATE VIEW FINANCE.BCRIXVA (
    T01CD,
    RIEDTCHC,
    RIENPCHC,
    T06CD ) AS
SELECT
    T1.T01CD,
    T1.RIEDTCHC,
    T1.RIENPCHC,
    T1.T06CD 
FROM FINANCE.BCRIXPT T1

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/36384/tddml/DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01.tddml.
DROP VIEW THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01
#WARNING#
Non è possibile eliminare l'oggetto 'THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01' di tipo vista, perché inesistente o perché non si dispone dell'autorizzazione.


********** #WARNING# ********** Definizione della vista non trovata
CREATE VIEW THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01 AS 

				SELECT DOC.*, 
				(
					CASE FAT.TIPO_DOC_ACQ_CTRL
						WHEN '3'
							THEN '(S)'
						WHEN '2'
							THEN '(T)'
						ELSE ''
					END
				) AS TIPO_DOC_ACQ_CTRL
				
				FROM THIP.DOC_ACQ_TES DOC  
				LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATACQ_DOCACQ FAT ON 
								DOC.ID_AZIENDA = FAT.ID_AZIENDA AND 
								DOC.ID_ANNO_DOC = FAT.ID_ANNO_DOC_ACQ  AND 
								DOC.ID_NUMERO_DOC  = FAT.ID_NUM_DOC_ACQ
GRANT ALL ON THIP.DOCACQ_FATCTRL_V01 TO PUBLIC

CREATE TABLE THERA.FAILED_LOGIN_LOG
(
   USER_ID CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   LOGIN_TIMESTAMP DATETIME NOT NULL,
   PASSWORD_TXT CHAR(20),
   IP_ADDRESS CHAR(250)
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX FAILED_LOGIN_L_I01 ON THERA.FAILED_LOGIN_LOG (USER_ID ASC, LOGIN_TIMESTAMP ASC)
ALTER TABLE THERA.FAILED_LOGIN_LOG ADD PRIMARY KEY  (USER_ID, LOGIN_TIMESTAMP)
GRANT ALL ON THERA.FAILED_LOGIN_LOG TO PUBLIC
